What you need to know:

Amanaka, 45, was found dead at his Maji Mazuri house in Nairobi's Kasarani estate on Friday by his younger brother James BarazaSpeaking to Nation Sport, Baraza said they got concerned when Amanaka could not be reached on phone for three days, prompting him to visit his house, where he found him deadDuring his heydays, Amanaka turned out for 11-time champions Tusker (formerly Kenya Breweries) and Kenya Pipeline